dcterms:creator: W. L. Hamilton
R. Ying
J. Leskovec
dcterms:description: A Reddit post network with each node representing a post, and each link indicating that the connected two posts are commonly commented by at least three users. User-averaged distributions of comments in different communities are used as link attributes.
dcterms:title: Reddit

dcterms:creator: W. L. Hamilton
R. Ying
J. Leskovec
dcterms:description: A co-author network constructed with papers from 2013 to 2017 in eight artificial intelligence conferences. The tf-idf vectors of paper titles are used as node attributes, and one-hot embeddings of common authors are used as link attributes.
dcterms:title: Dblp

dcterms:creator: W. L. Hamilton
R. Ying
J. Leskovec
dcterms:description: A temporal network constructed with user contacts in email services. The contacts of exact times are discretized into time-slices and used as link attributes. Node features are represented by embeddings obtained from transductive LINE.
dcterms:title: Email

dcterms:creator: W. L. Hamilton
R. Ying
J. Leskovec
dcterms:description: A temporal network constructed with user contacts in mobile-phone services. Similar to the email dataset, the contacts of exact times are discretized into time-slices and used as link attributes. Node features are represented by embeddings obtained from transductive LINE.
dcterms:title: Fmobile
